    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718920/extras/ae730b9303da7442d519acca56a0bfb5.avif?t=1709231190\" width=600 height=82 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718920/extras/3eb4f9cdd701f304486a93f69f16347e.poster.avif?t=1709231190\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718920/extras/3eb4f9cdd701f304486a93f69f16347e.webm?t=1709231190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718920/extras/3eb4f9cdd701f304486a93f69f16347e.mp4?t=1709231190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Mega Monster Party is a classic multiplayer board game and minigame collection by AirConsole, perfect for passing time and ending friendships! <br>Players use their smartphones as gamepads to control one of eight monstrous characters and conquer the board. <br><br>Choose paths wisely, use secret items to gain advantage and stock up on coins by winning PvP minigames. Once you have the funds, find the Board Master and trade coins for monster minions to get ready for the multiplayer final battle. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718920/extras/d1cfdd4b162281c5b8100d9829b33313.avif?t=1709231190\" width=600 height=82 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718920/extras/b32c0bd62f1a533b15a0676d810611c1.poster.avif?t=1709231190\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718920/extras/b32c0bd62f1a533b15a0676d810611c1.webm?t=1709231190\"